[TaskChampion][1] is the task database [Taskwarrior][2] uses to store and sync
tasks. [Taskchampion Sync-Server][3] implements a sync server against which
Taskwarrior and other applications embedding TaskChampion can sync.

[1]: https://github.com/GothenburgBitFactory/taskchampion
[2]: https://github.com/GothenburgBitFactory/taskwarrior
[3]: https://github.com/GothenburgBitFactory/taskchampion-sync-server
